## Open core + managed service

This repository contains the **open-source core** of Qubox:
- WebRTC-style signaling
- Device pairing and identity (Ed25519)
- Native QUIC and WebRTC transports
- Desktop host agent, daemon, CLI, and Tauri GUI
- Cross-platform media pipeline (Linux / Windows / macOS)

A **managed SaaS** is offered at <https://qubox.app> that adds:
- Account and device enrollment database
- Stripe billing and Pro plan
- Multi-tenant org workspaces
- Hosted regional TURN fleet
- Hosted TUF auto-update channel
- Status page, observability, and dashboards

The managed service is **not** part of this repository. It is
implemented in a separate, private codebase that integrates with the
open signaling and desktop clients over the same wire protocols.

