## Third-party components

This project reuses open-source components; see the Cargo.lock for
exact crate versions and `apps/qubox-client-gui/package-lock.json` for
the GUI's npm dependencies. All dependencies are used under their
respective licenses (MIT / Apache-2.0 / BSD-2-Clause / etc.).

A non-exhaustive list of notable dependencies:

- `tokio` — MIT
- `axum` — MIT
- `quinn` — MIT
- `wgpu` — MIT/Apache-2.0
- `tauri` — MIT/Apache-2.0
- `serde` / `serde_json` — MIT/Apache-2.0
- `cpal`, `opus`, `pipewire` bindings — MIT/Apache-2.0 / LGPL variants
- `nokhwa` (and friends) — see upstream

The TUF implementation uses concepts from The Update Framework
(<https://theupdateframework.com/>); see `docs/tuf.md` for details.

